author: COMSOL
description: This tutorial describes a drying case with laminar airflow through an unsaturated porous medium. The air is dry at the inlet and its moisture content increases as air flows through the porous medium. The water saturation in the porous medium is computed over time. It is supposed that water leaves the potato sample only as vapor.
